This '''space station''', located over the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Yag'Dhul/Legends|Yag'Dhul]], was used as the base of the [[Yag'Dhul insurgents]] around [[5 BBY/Legends|5 BBY]]. In that [[Standard year/Legends|year]], the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] [[Battle of Yag'Dhul (Imperial era)|attacked]] the insurgents, and during the battle, the space station was destroyed.

